#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.from_dict.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.from\\_dict"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:1 of
msgid "Construct DataFrame from dict of array-like or dicts."
msgstr "从 array-like 或 dict 的字典构造 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:3 of
msgid ""
"Creates DataFrame object from dictionary by columns or by index allowing "
"dtype specification."
msgstr "通过列或索引从字典创建 DataFrame 对象，允许指定数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:6 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Of the form {field : array-like} or {field : dict}."
msgstr "形式为 {field : array-like} 或 {field : dict}。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:8 of
msgid ""
"The \"orientation\" of the data. If the keys of the passed dict should be"
" the columns of the resulting DataFrame, pass 'columns' (default). "
"Otherwise if the keys should be rows, pass 'index'. If 'tight', assume a "
"dict with keys ['index', 'columns', 'data', 'index_names', "
"'column_names']."
msgstr ""
"数据的“方向”。如果传入的字典的键应该是结果 DataFrame 的列，请传递 '"
"columns'（默认）。如果键应该是行，请传递 'index'。如果为 'tight'，则假定"
"字典包含键 ['index', 'columns', 'data', 'index_names', 'column_names']。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:14 of
msgid "Data type to force after DataFrame construction, otherwise infer."
msgstr "在 DataFrame 构造后强制使用的数据类型，否则进行推断。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:16 of
msgid ""
"Column labels to use when ``orient='index'``. Raises a ValueError if used"
" with ``orient='columns'`` or ``orient='tight'``."
msgstr ""
"当 ``orient='index'`` 时使用的列标签。如果与 ``orient='columns'`` 或 ``"
"orient='tight'`` 一起使用会引发 ValueError。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.from_records`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:25 of
msgid ""
"DataFrame from structured ndarray, sequence of tuples or dicts, or "
"DataFrame."
msgstr "从结构化 ndarray、元组或字典序列，或 DataFrame 构造 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:28 of
msgid "DataFrame object creation using constructor."
msgstr "使用构造函数创建 DataFrame 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:30 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.to_dict`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:31 of
msgid "Convert the DataFrame to a dictionary."
msgstr "将 DataFrame 转换为字典。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:34 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:35 of
msgid "By default the keys of the dict become the DataFrame columns:"
msgstr "默认情况下，字典的键将成为 DataFrame 的列："

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:46 of
msgid ""
"Specify ``orient='index'`` to create the DataFrame using dictionary keys "
"as rows:"
msgstr "指定 ``orient='index'`` 以使用字典键作为行来创建 DataFrame："

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:55 of
msgid ""
"When using the 'index' orientation, the column names can be specified "
"manually:"
msgstr "使用 'index' 方向时，可以手动指定列名："

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.from_dict.dataframe_from_dict:64 of
msgid "Specify ``orient='tight'`` to create the DataFrame using a 'tight' format:"
msgstr "指定 ``orient='tight'`` 以使用 'tight' 格式创建 DataFrame："

